 availability constraints. CVN 75 cost decrease is due to realized hardware cost savings.

 CARRIER INTELLIGENCE CENTER (CVIC) RIPOUT/INSTALL: CVN 74 cost increase is due to transition of infrastructure work scope as a result initial contractor's poor performance. Transition to new contactor
 required rescoping of remaining effort, significant corrective rework, and material procurements. Impacts were experienced by multiple C4I tasks, including indirect impacts due to resultant space availability
 constraints.

