 incurred costs. The CVN 75 RCOH includes sixteen unlisted systems, each under $1 million in major hardware requirement. The most significant difference between CVN 74 and CVN 75 is the re-categorization
 of Habitability Program Management and OSIC (On-site Installation Coordinator) efforts from Basic Construction/Conversion for CVN 74 to HM&E for CVN 75.




