 B KITS: AN/ALQ-99 TJS hardware procurements include the continued accelerated procurement of Low Band Consolidation (LBC) transmitters, Band 9/10 Power Supply Group (PSG), transmitters, Modernized
 Universal Exciter Upgrade (M-UEU), Patagium antennas for various transmitters (LBC, Low Band Transmitter, Band 5/6, etc.) to address specific known threats as well as other AN/ALQ-99 TJS transmitters and
 antenna.

