 Description:
 The AN/SLQ-32 Surface Electronic Warfare Improvement Program (SEWIP)V(7) provides DDG 51 Class Destroyers with the electronic warfare capability of automatically detecting, sorting, classifying, tracking,
 engaging and continually displaying emitter and platform densities of anti-ship missiles (ASM). The AN/SLQ-32(V)7 (also called SEWIP Block 3) also provides advanced electronic attack capability to keep pace
 with the evolving ASM threat and counter-targeting.

