 Digital Fire Control System (DFCS), a crucial enhancement that will secure a vital combat advantage for our maneuver forces. This investment will equip our warfighters with the ability to provide relentless,
 precision fire support under all conditions day or night, in any weather, and even in GPS-denied combat zones. As the sole cannon in the service, directly enhancing the lethality and operational readiness of the
 M777A2 is paramount to sustaining our warfighting capabilities and ensuring our forces can deliver the decisive fires critical to mission success.$$, $$$$, $$Exhibit P-40, Budget Line Item Justification: PB 2027 Navy                                                                                                                              Date: April 2026
